# Data Flow Diagram


## Project Flow (Level 0 DFD)

```
 [Farmer / User]
        │  (N, P, K, temperature, humidity, pH, rainfall)
        ▼
 ┌───────────────────────┐
 │ 1. Web Interface       │  (HTML/CSS/JS form)
 │    Collect Input        │
 └──────────┬────────────┘
            ▼
 ┌───────────────────────┐
 │ 2. Flask Backend        │  Validate & format input
 │    Process Request      │
 └──────────┬────────────┘
            ▼
 ┌───────────────────────┐        ┌─────────────────────┐
 │ 3. Trained ML Model     │◄──────┤ Model Store          │
 │    (KNN / Logistic       │      │ best_model.pkl        │
 │     Regression / K-Means)│      └─────────────────────┘
 └──────────┬────────────┘
            ▼
 ┌───────────────────────┐
 │ 4. Generate Prediction  │  Recommended crop + confidence
 └──────────┬────────────┘
            ▼
 [Farmer / User] ◄── Recommendation displayed on results page
```

## DFD Symbol Legend

| Symbol | Name | Description |
|---|---|---|
| Oval/Rounded shape | External Entity | Farmer/User who submits soil & climate data and receives the recommendation |
| Numbered rectangle | Process | Web Interface, Flask Backend, ML Model Inference, Prediction Generation |
| Solid rectangle | Data Store | Trained model file (`best_model.pkl`), crop dataset (`crop_dataset.csv`) |
| Labeled arrow | Data Flow | N/P/K/temperature/humidity/pH/rainfall values → prediction result |
